The problem of extraordinary threats, excluding extreme hydrometeorological hazards, requires to take into consideration also other serious threats resulting from the civilization development (technical catastrophes, technological breakdowns and synergic threats whose number increases). These problems should be considered jointly. In this scope some works have already began and they will be continued. They cover: 
-assessment of threats occurring in the country, including identification of threat sources, break down of extreme threats and their characteristics; 
-definition of the state of extreme threats protection systems, taking into account prevention actions (including solutions applied abroad).

